learning dom manipulation

      /*   */
      /**
 * The Calculator class provides basic math operations.
 */
public class Calculator {

    /**
     * Adds two numbers together.
     * @param a the first number
     * @param b the second number
     * @return the sum of a and b
     */
    public int add(int a, int b) {
        return a + b;
    }

    /**
     * Subtracts one number from another.
     * @param a the first number
     * @param b the number to subtract
     * @return the result of a - b
     */
    public int subtract(int a, int b) {
        return a - b;
    }
}

Special Tags in Javadoc

@param → describes a method parameter

@return → describes what the method returns

@throws → describes exceptions that the method might throw

@author → author of the code

@version → version info

⚡ In short:

// → single line

/* ... */ → multi-line

/** ... */ → Javadoc (for documentation, can generate HTML docs)